Edit Cultural Object Data

To edit the Cultural Object select the Edit action

The Cultural Object opens in Edit mode. In Edit mode of the Cultural Object you can:

  1. Add additional sections and text at the landing page
  2. Format the free text by using the document formatting controls at the top of the page or add additional widgets to present additional data in the selected tab

Once open for editing the cultural object becomes locked for editing by other system users. All other user will be able to edit the cultural object when you save the cultural object.

      4. To save the cultural object press the Save button.
